---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TopNav from "../../components/TopNav.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="隐私政策 - Trending AI"
    description="Trending AI 隐私政策"
    canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
    <TopNav />
    <main class="pt-20 pb-16 px-4">
        <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose">
            <h1>隐私政策</h1>
            <p class="text-secondary">最后更新：2026 年 3 月 23 日</p>

            <p>
                Trending AI（以下简称"我们"）重视您的隐私。本政策说明我们在您使用 Trending AI
                应用程序及网站（trendingai.cn）时如何收集、使用和保护您的信息。
            </p>

            <h2>我们收集的信息</h2>

            <h3>基础使用数据</h3>
            <p>
                我们通过 Aptabase（一款注重隐私的分析工具）收集匿名使用统计，包括：
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>应用启动次数</li>
                <li>会话时长</li>
                <li>功能使用情况（如筛选条件的选择）</li>
            </ul>
            <p>这些数据不包含任何可识别个人身份的信息。</p>

            <h3>用户偏好设置</h3>
            <p>
                我们在您的设备本地存储以下偏好设置，这些数据不会上传至服务器：
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>主题模式（浅色 / 深色 / 跟随系统）</li>
                <li>语言偏好</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>API 请求参数</h3>
            <p>
                当您浏览内容时，应用会向我们的服务器发送必要的请求参数（如时间周期、编程语言筛选等），
                用于返回您需要的数据。这些参数不与任何用户身份关联。
            </p>

            <h2>我们不收集的信息</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>个人身份信息（姓名、邮箱、手机号等）</li>
                <li>设备唯一标识符（Device ID、IMEI、ANDROID_ID 等）</li>
                <li>地理位置信息</li>
                <li>联系人、日历、文件等敏感数据</li>
                <li>应用不要求注册或登录账号</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>数据共享</h2>
            <p>
                我们不会出售、出租或以其他方式向第三方分享您的个人数据。匿名使用统计通过 Aptabase
                处理，Aptabase 遵循严格的数据保护标准。
            </p>

            <h2>数据安全</h2>
            <p>
                所有网络通信均使用 HTTPS 加密。用户偏好数据仅存储在您的设备本地。
            </p>

            <h2>儿童隐私</h2>
            <p>
                我们的应用不针对 13 岁以下的儿童，也不会故意收集儿童的个人信息。
            </p>

            <h2>隐私政策的更新</h2>
            <p>
                我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策。更新后的政策将在本页面发布，并更新顶部的"最后更新"日期。
            </p>

            <h2>联系我们</h2>
            <p>
                如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问，请通过以下方式联系我们：
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>GitHub：<a href="https://github.com/HarlonWang/TrendingAI/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">提交 Issue</a></li>
            </ul>

            <hr />

            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="text-secondary">Last Updated: March 23, 2026</p>

            <p>
                Trending AI ("we") values your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and
                protect your information when you use the Trending AI app and website (trendingai.cn).
            </p>

            <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

            <h3>Basic Usage Data</h3>
            <p>
                We collect anonymous usage statistics through Aptabase, a privacy-focused analytics tool,
                including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>App launch count</li>
                <li>Session duration</li>
                <li>Feature usage (e.g., filter selections)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>This data does not contain any personally identifiable information.</p>

            <h3>User Preferences</h3>
            <p>
                The following preferences are stored locally on your device and are never uploaded to our
                servers:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Theme mode (light / dark / system)</li>
                <li>Language preference</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>API Request Parameters</h3>
            <p>
                When you browse content, the app sends necessary request parameters (such as time period
                and programming language filters) to our servers to return the data you need. These
                parameters are not associated with any user identity.
            </p>

            <h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal identity information (name, email, phone number, etc.)</li>
                <li>Device identifiers (Device ID, IMEI, ANDROID_ID, etc.)</li>
                <li>Geographic location</li>
                <li>Contacts, calendar, files, or other sensitive data</li>
                <li>The app does not require registration or login</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
            <p>
                We do not sell, rent, or otherwise share your personal data with third parties. Anonymous
                usage statistics are processed through Aptabase, which follows strict data protection
                standards.
            </p>

            <h2>Data Security</h2>
            <p>
                All network communications are encrypted using HTTPS. User preference data is stored only
                on your device.
            </p>

            <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>
                Our app is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
                information from children.
            </p>

            <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Updated policies will be posted on
                this page with a revised "Last Updated" date.
            </p>

            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/HarlonWang/TrendingAI/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open an Issue</a></li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </main>
    <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .prose {
        color: var(--color-on-surface);
        line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .prose h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: var(--color-on-surface);
    }
    .prose h1:first-child {
        margin-top: 0;
    }
    .prose h2 {
        font-size: 1.375rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--color-on-surface);
    }
    .prose h3 {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--color-on-surface);
    }
    .prose p {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .prose ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .prose li {
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .prose a {
        color: var(--color-primary);
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .prose hr {
        margin: 3rem 0;
        border-color: var(--color-outline-variant);
    }
    .text-secondary {
        color: var(--color-on-surface-variant);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
    }
</style>
